verses.verse: A Song <WH7892> of degrees <WH4609>. Behold, bless <WH1288> ye the LORD <WH3068>, all ye servants <WH5650> of the LORD <WH3068>, which by night <WH3915> stand <WH5975> in the house <WH1004> of the LORD <WH3068>.
Lift up <WH5375> your hands <WH3027> in the sanctuary <WH6944>, and bless <WH1288> the LORD <WH3068>.
The LORD <WH3068> that made <WH6213> heaven <WH8064> and earth <WH776> bless <WH1288> thee out of Zion <WH6726>.
